# CSS Transforms

Transforms change an element's shape, size, or position.

## Rotate

```css
div {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
}
```

## Scale

```css
div {
    transform: scale(1.2);
}
```

## Translate

```css
div {
    transform: translateX(50px);
}
```

## Skew

```css
div {
    transform: skew(10deg);
}
```

## Real-World Example

Cards often enlarge when hovered.

```css
.card:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
}
```

## Summary

Transforms create engaging UI interactions.
